instructions: Place the dinner plate right side up on the table.
Place a single dinner fork on the left side of the plate.
Place a salad fork next to the dinner fork.
Place a dinner knife on the right side of the plate
Place a salad knife next to the dinner knife.
Place a soup spoon next to the salad knife.
Place a water glass on the right side of the plate slightly behind the dinner knife.
Place a wine glass on the right side of the water glass.
Place a second wine glass to the right of the first one.
Place a coffee cup to the right of the soup spoon.
Place a bread plate just behind the forks
Place a butter knife on the bread plate.
Place a dessert fork just behind the dinner plate between the cutlery on either side.
Place a dessert spoon next to the dessert fork.
Place a neatly rolled napkin vertically aligned in the middle of the dinner plate.
